Greg Martin: "Players who use Warcraft, Everquest, Ultima and others sell their money to other gamers in exchange for real cash. There are auction sites devoted to facilitating these exchanges, including exchanges between completely different games through the medium of regular money. You can even look up exchange rates between various game currencies and the US dollar."


